WEBVTT

00:06.040 --> 00:08.440
Her name is Melanie Jaswinsky.

00:10.044 --> 00:11.978
Single shot, small caliber,

00:11.979 --> 00:13.479
point blank to the throat.

00:13.481 --> 00:15.581
The last thing she saw
on God's green earth

00:15.583 --> 00:17.150
was her killer's face.

00:17.151 --> 00:18.851
I hope it was good-looking.

00:18.852 --> 00:20.987
Purse was found near the body.

00:20.988 --> 00:22.818
One of those big satchel jobs.

00:22.823 --> 00:23.963
Contents were gone.

00:23.964 --> 00:26.657
Lab found traces of cocaine,

00:26.660 --> 00:27.994
yellowish in color.

00:27.995 --> 00:29.725
The good shit.

00:29.730 --> 00:31.130
Drug deal went south?

00:31.132 --> 00:33.502
No prints, no witnesses,
no weapon.

00:33.503 --> 00:37.108
We got nothing but a pretty
girl with a hole in her throat.

00:37.109 --> 00:38.505
Kick it over to Narcotics.

00:38.506 --> 00:40.236
City controller
is busting my stones

00:40.241 --> 00:42.841
on all the overtime hours
logged last pay period.

00:42.843 --> 00:44.043
All right.

00:51.018 --> 00:52.788
Hey, out there in
radioland, you're listening

00:52.789 --> 00:54.286
to the best station in Stockton.

00:54.288 --> 00:55.657
Don't touch that dial.

00:55.658 --> 00:58.156
The station that makes
you want to listen.

01:01.129 --> 01:02.359
Here's what's happening.

01:02.363 --> 01:04.032
A 39-year-old unidentified man

01:04.033 --> 01:05.669
went berserk last night...

01:05.670 --> 01:07.396
- Where are you?
- Car broke down.

01:07.401 --> 01:09.171
What am I supposed to do
until you get here?

01:09.172 --> 01:10.370
You have to stall.

01:10.371 --> 01:12.439
Wilson, don't wait for Apex.

01:12.440 --> 01:13.870
I need you to get in your car...

01:13.874 --> 01:15.144
Too late. He's here.

01:15.145 --> 01:16.943
Stay on the line.

01:16.944 --> 01:18.750
Are not
releasing any information

01:18.751 --> 01:20.746
until they complete
their investigation.

01:20.748 --> 01:22.978
- You Apex?
- Got the money?

01:22.983 --> 01:24.253
It's on the way.

01:26.254 --> 01:28.064
Suspect's death.

